From 1228d99fac4c103a1ca6af82ddd27ba2c445d0ca Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Jeff Johnson <jeff.johnson@oss.qualcomm.com>
Date: Sun, 20 Jul 2025 08:13:38 -0700
Subject: [PATCH] wifi: ath11k: Prefer {} to {0} in initializers
Git-commit: 1228d99fac4c103a1ca6af82ddd27ba2c445d0ca
Patch-mainline: v6.17-rc1
References: jsc#PED-14425

Prefer {} to {0} in initializers since {} works even when the first
member is not a scalar.

Generated using:
sed -i 's/{[[:space:]]*0[[:space:]]*}/{}/g' drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath11k/*

Compile tested only.

Link: https://patch.msgid.link/20250720-ath11k-zero-brace-v1-1-6132e2ef1748@oss.qualcomm.com
Signed-off-by: Jeff Johnson <jeff.johnson@oss.qualcomm.com>
Acked-by: Takashi Iwai <tiwai@suse.de>

